title: Bug 121682: Exception thrown when exporting data from a table containing highlight/map
description: Exception occurs when attempting to export data from an attached report.
OB: When trying to export the data from a table in the attached report, an exception is thrown.
EB: I expected that when I export the data from the table, the operation would complete successfully without any errors.
SR: Steps to reproduce: 1. Open the attached report. 2. Go to the table containing highlight/map. 3. Attempt to export the data from the table.
